<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-64-0128 </DOCNO><TEXT>The storage ring Adone has been recently equipped with a new beam positiondetecting system consisting of 21 electrostatic pick-up monitors. Absoluteaccuracy is andless;0.2 mm with respect to the center of the nearby quadrupole.Reproducibility is within 0.025 mm. The position measurements are usedto correct the closed orbit distortion by a least squares minimization.</TEXT></DOC>